# Quality Gates & Validation

> **Version:** 1.0.0 | **Category:** Cat 6 (Corrections) | **TrigMem Auto-Load**
> **Triggers:** "quality gate", "acceptance criteria", "validation checklist", "ready to merge"
> **Last Updated:** 2026-03-18

---

## 🎯 Universal Quality Gates

**Apply to ALL implementation tasks:**

| Gate | Verification | Command |
|------|-------------|---------|
| Code compiles | Build successful | `npm run build` |
| Type checks pass | No type errors | `npm run typecheck` |
| Lint passes | No lint errors | `npm run lint` |
| Format passes | No format errors | `pnpm run fmt:check` (oxfmt) |
| Tests pass | All tests green | `npm test` |
| No regressions | Existing tests pass | `npm test` |

---

## 🏗️ Quality Gates by Task Type

### Feature Development

- [ ] **E1** - User requirement met
- [ ] **E2** - Integration successful
- [ ] **E3** - No breaking changes
- [ ] **E4** - Tests passing
- [ ] **E5** - Documentation updated

### Bug Fix

- [ ] **B1** - Root cause identified
- [ ] **B2** - Fix applied (not symptom)
- [ ] **B3** - Regression test added
- [ ] **B4** - Tests pass
- [ ] **B5** - No side effects

### Refactoring

- [ ] **R1** - Behavior preserved
- [ ] **R2** - Tests pass
- [ ] **R3** - Code reduced
- [ ] **R4** - Complexity reduced
- [ ] **R5** - No regressions

### Performance Optimization

- [ ] **P1** - Baseline measured
- [ ] **P2** - Improvement verified (≥20%)
- [ ] **P3** - Target met
- [ ] **P4** - No regressions
- [ ] **P5** - Stability maintained

---

## ✅ Pre-Delivery Checklist

### Core Verification
- [ ] Code compiles
- [ ] Type checks pass
- [ ] Lint passes
- [ ] Tests pass
- [ ] No console errors/warnings

### Task-Specific
- [ ] Quality gates for task type applied
- [ ] Acceptance criteria satisfied

### Final
- [ ] Modified files listed
- [ ] File references included
- [ ] Next steps clear

---

## 📊 Success Metrics

| Task Type | Success Metric | Target |
|-----------|----------------|--------|
| Feature | User requirement coverage | 100% |
| Bug Fix | Bug cannot be reproduced | 100% |
| Refactor | Code reduction / Complexity down | ≥10% |
| Performance | Performance improvement | ≥20% |
| Security | Vulnerability eliminated | 100% |

